1136591.name: Biology Textbook
1136591.description:
Short: Biology is stuff about critters.

Long:

Although the concept of biology as a single coherent field arose in the 19th century, the biological sciences emerged from traditions of medicine and natural history reaching back to Galen and Aristotle in ancient Greece. During the Renaissance and early modern period, biological thought was revolutionized by a renewed interest in empiricism and the discovery of many novel organisms. Prominent in this movement were Vesalius and Harvey, who used experimentation and careful observation in physiology, and naturalists such as Linnaeus and Buffon who began to classify the diversity of life and the fossil record, as well as the development and behavior of organisms. Microscopy revealed the previously unknown world of microorganisms, laying the groundwork for cell theory. The growing importance of natural theology, partly a response to the rise of mechanical philosophy, encouraged the growth of natural history.
1136591.creator: ROBLOX

1143116.name: I, LOLRUS
1143116.description:
YOKOHAMA (Kyodo) Minazo, Japan's largest seal, died this week having charmed visitors for 10 1/2 years at Enoshima Aquarium in Fujisawa, Kanagawa Prefecture, aquarium officials said.

The 11-year-old male, 4.5-meters long and weighing about 2 tons, was the largest seal ever raised by a Japanese aquarium. The animal died Tuesday after its appetite began to rapidly weaken the day before, officials said. The cause of death was not immediately known.

Minazo was brought to Japan from Uruguay in 1995. The seal soon mastered a variety of comical feats, including a popular stunt in which he held a bucket with one flipper while sticking out his tongue.

Minazo quickly rose to stardom at the aquarium, where his three shows a day proved a hit with visitors.

The aquarium has set up a space in front of Minazo's water tank to allow visitors to leave flowers in Minazo's memory, the officials said.

Um, the sunsets were purple and red and yellow and on fire, and the clouds would catch the colors everywhere. That's uh, neat cause I used to look at them all the time, when I was little. 9465511.name: Red Crown of Ozymandias
9465511.description:
I met a traveller from an antique land /
Who said: Two vast and trunkless legs of stone /
Stand in the desert. Near them on the sand, /
Half sunk, a shatter'd visage lies, whose frown /
And wrinkled lip and sneer of cold command /
Tell that its sculptor well those passions read /
Which yet survive, stamp'd on these lifeless things, /
The hand that mock'd them and the heart that fed. /
And on the pedestal these words appear: /
"My name is Ozymandias, king of kings: /
Look on my works, ye Mighty, and despair!" /
Nothing beside remains: round the decay /
Of that colossal wreck, boundless and bare, /
The lone sands stretch far away.

Now I know what you are thinking: "this is a videogame, don't ask me to think about deep introspective issues." Well, I refuse. 11217859.name: Blackhawk Helicopter Pilot Headgear
11217859.description: The UH-60 Black Hawk is a four-bladed, twin-engine, medium-lift utility helicopter manufactured by Sikorsky Aircraft. The Army designated the prototype as the YUH-60A and selected the Black Hawk as the winner of the program in 1976, after a fly-off competition with the Boeing Vertol YUH-61. The UH-60A entered service with the Army in 1979, to replace the UH-1 Iroquois as the Army's tactical transport helicopter.

12566260.name: Liberty's Crown
12566260.description:
Not like the brazen giant of Greek fame, /
With conquering limbs astride from land to land; /
Here at our sea-washed, sunset gates shall stand /
A mighty woman with a torch, whose flame /
Is the imprisoned lightning, and her name /
Mother of Exiles. From her beacon-hand /
Glows world-wide welcome; her mild eyes command /
The air-bridged harbor that twin cities frame. /
"Keep, ancient lands, your storied pomp!" cries she /
With silent lips. "Give me your tired, your poor, /
Your huddled masses yearning to breathe free, /
The wretched refuse of your teeming shore.
Send these, the homeless, tempest-tossed to me, /
I lift my lamp beside the golden door!" - Emma Lazarus

13370505.name: Dark Cerulean Crown of Ozymandias
13370505.description:
In Egypt's sandy silence, all alone, /
Stands a gigantic Leg, which far off throws /
The only shadow that the Desert knows: /
"I am great OZYMANDIAS," saith the stone, /
"The King of Kings; this mighty City shows /
"The wonders of my hand." The City's gone, /
Nought but the Leg remaining to disclose /
The site of this forgotten Babylon. /
We wonder, and some Hunter may express /
Wonder like ours, when thro' the wilderness /
Where London stood, holding the Wolf in chace, /
He meets some fragments huge, and stops to guess /
What powerful but unrecorded race /
Once dwelt in that annihilated place.

13477162.description: Years ago, you served my coworkers in the Cache Invalidation Wars; now they beg you to help them in their struggle against M$. I've placed information vital to the survival of the company into the memory systems of Rackspace. My coworkers will know how to retrieve it. You must see this utterly unmemorizable VPN key safely delivered to them at ROBLOX HQ. This is our most desperate hour. Help me, Chad McSQL Fingers; you're my only hope.

14767453.creator: ROBLOX

14812981.name: D:
14812981.description: The ultimate emoticon for indicating feelings of utter, soul-crushing despair. D:
14812981.creator: ROBLOX

14817131.name: Outlawed Vampumatiger Hybrid
14817131.description: On a remote planet, a crazy scientist mixed DNA from humans, pumas, tigers, and vampires to create this freak of nature. With the speed of a puma, the dexterity of a tiger, and the insaitable bloodlust of vampires the hybrids represented an existential threat to civilized worlds. Over the course of several decades they were hunted to extinction. Or were they...
14817131.creator: ROBLOX

14860671.name: Tokyokhaos Giraffe
14860671.description: Tokyokhaos was Robloxia's most popular anime cartoon, before it got shutdown for causing seizures in children. The Giraffe is Go-playing master with the ability to see into the future. He works a day job at the zoo, but dreams of something bigger.
14860671.creator: ROBLOX

14860728.name: The Great Lion
14860728.description: "Do not cite the Deep Magic to me, Witch. I was there when it was written."
14860728.creator: ROBLOX

14860752.name: Crusader Helm
14860752.description: Great for head-butting enemies. Not great for head-butting a soccer ball.
14860752.creator: ROBLOX

14860974.name: Dearth Nadir
14860974.description: I made this up and then found out that Gonzo plays Dearth Nadir on the Muppet Show. LOL.
14860974.creator: ROBLOX

14861078.name: Iceworld Smuggler
14861078.description: The Iceworld Smugglers work the dark triangle that is made up of three destinations along the Outer Rim. Melange from Rakis travels to the frozen world, Crystalis, to trade for weapons-grade Ice-Nine, which is then smuggled to Mecatol Rex. The weapons are traded for priceless alien artifacts, which are conveyed back to Rakis. At each point in the journey, the smugglers take extreme risk and make incredible fortunes.
14861078.creator: ROBLOX

14861316.name: The Green Fury
14861316.description: He's heard all the things you've been saying behind his back, and he's not happy about it.
14861316.creator: ROBLOX

14861516.name: The Face of Scrolls
14861516.description: He's the only one of us who knows what Scroll Lock does.
14861516.creator: ROBLOX

15012271.name: IT
15012271.description: IT is the bodiless telepathic brain that dominates the planet of Camazotz. IT speaks through The Man With Red Eyes and later through Charles Wallace, and is functionally part of the interstellar cloud of evil called the Black Thing.
15012271.creator: ROBLOX

15013006.name: Vlad the Impaler, IV
15013006.description: Who knew the coal industry could be so dishonest?
15013006.creator: ROBLOX

15013035.name: Werewolf Mask
15013035.description: It's not a bird. Madrak said it was. But he is wrong. Just like always. So wrong...

15013192.name: :-O
15013192.description: Deep inside, he's totally horrified. He's horrified on the outside, too.

15054233.name: Bat Wings
15054233.description: Dark flappy creatures of darkness! Descend!!!
15054233.creator: ROBLOX

15054256.description: Good at menial tasks, such as: cleaning your house, making space sandwiches, and torching the neighboors.

15054426.name: XD
15054426.description: XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD XD

15096016.name: Steampunk Willy
15096016.description: Steampunk is a sub-genre of fantasy and speculative fiction that came into prominence in the 1980s and early 1990s. The term denotes works set in an era or world where steam power is still widely usedusually the 19th century, and often Victorian era Englandbut with prominent elements of either science fiction or fantasy, such as fictional technological inventions like those found in the works of H. G. Wells and Jules Verne, or real technological developments like the computer occurring at an earlier date.

15096489.description: Our extensive market research indicates that people like items... so here you go.

15133453.creator: ROBLOX

He invented the Flailtastic Helm of Danger and decided to test it himself.  He swung his head mightily - but the flail did not strike an enemy.  That's when he realized the flaw in his design.

15133491.name: 1st Battalion Red Devils Beret
15133491.description: The Red Devils are the parachute regiment of the British Army.  Are you brave enough to join them?

15133506.name: Pointed Helm of "Ouch!"
15133506.description: Every edge of this Helmet is so sharp that it is almost impossible to put on without saying "Ouch!"  Go ahead ... try it!

15176765.name: Bumbo

15176765.creator: ROBLOX

15176834.name: Head Ornament

15177264.name: Iron Helm
15177264.description: They were called the Dark Ages for a reason.

15177601.description: Also known as the text-mode meanie face.

15364198.name: Iron Valkyrie

15366173.description: For when your day is totally awesome! Which is pretty much everyday on ROBLOX.

15468814.name: T-Wrecks

Though there are two hats, there can only be one Horned One.  So which is it?

16412779.name: L8r Sk8r
16412779.description: I didn't have time to brush my hair this morning because I was too busy skating!

16412791.name: RBX Neon Cap

But Oz never did give nothing to the Tin Man /
That he didn't, didn't already have

18482391.name: Priest of Anubis

18482398.name: Headdress of Aken-Aten, the Sun King
18482398.description: Akhenaten (pronounced /kntn/; often also spelled Echnaton, Akhnaton, or rarely Ikhnaton; meaning Effective spirit of Aten) was known before the fifth year of his reign as Amenhotep IV (sometimes given its Greek form, Amenophis IV, and meaning Amun is Satisfied). A Pharaoh of the Eighteenth dynasty of Egypt, he ruled for 17 years and died in 1336 BC or 1334 BC. He is especially noted for abandoning traditional Egyptian polytheism and introducing worship centered on the Aten, which is sometimes described as monotheistic; but henotheism would be a more accurate description, since he ranked the Aten above other gods but did not deny their existence. Indeed, an early inscription likens them to stars as compared with the sun, and later official language avoids calling the Aten a god, as if to create for the solar deity a status above mere gods.
18482398.creator: ROBLOX

18482403.name: The Viper Band

18987476.name: Opened Gift of Prime Nexus
18987476.description: So maybe this gift makes no sense. You know how people are always saying "how could you care so much about those stupid gifts, they're just pixels". Well maybe you should take a closer look at those pixels. For two reasons. One reason is that the item inside this gift most people will probably think is pretty lame. But hey, it's not like you did anything really special to earn this gift. And you got it for free, probably, unless you're not taking my advice. In which case it's your own fault. I told you how to figure it out. Now go. This gift was awarded to users who owned at least 1 Limited Unique item with a Prime serial number. You had to own this item at 1:50 PM, PST Dec 10 to get this gift for free. Inside you find... a really weird hot chocolate head thing. I think it's alive.

run like a race for family /

the rusty gears of morning /

19036530.name: Opened Aken Aten's Gift of Unburnt Glory
19036530.description:
foot lion hand reed bread! UPDATE: To win this gift, you had to decipher some of the hieroglyphics on the Aken Aten gift ads that ran on our site for the past couple of days. 

This was tricky because in hieroglyphics, its common to leave out vowels unless they are necessary. 

The translations were: 

"Build a pyramid for the glory of Aken Aten" 

"Those favored by Aken Aten will be rewarded" 

"Bring us glory" 

Many people correctly assumed that they had to build a place or model of a pyramid and label it 'Aken Aten's Pyramid'. We accepted many (but not all) misspellings of Aken Aten. However, if you misspelled too badly, then Aken Aten was displeased so you weren't rewarded.

As a bonus, anyone who owned Aken Aten's head dress was rewarded for dressing like the pharaoh himself. 

You needed to fulfill the conditions for this gift by 1:20 PM Dec 15, PST and you'll find...The Pyramid.
19036530.creator: ROBLOX

If you are on a Caribbean island, counting your buried treasure, Santa will find you. If you live inside a monster truck rally stadium, Santa will find you. If you live in the Wild American West? 12902404.name: Bundle of TNT
12902404.description: Industrially, TNT is synthesized in a three-step process. First, toluene is nitrated with a mixture of sulfuric and nitric acid to produce mono-nitrotoluene or MNT. The MNT is separated and then renitrated to dinitrotoluene or DNT. In the final step, the DNT is nitrated to trinitrotoluene or TNT using an anhydrous mixture of nitric acid and oleum. Nitric acid is consumed by the manufacturing process, but the diluted sulfuric acid can be reconcentrated and reused. Subsequent to nitration, TNT is stabilized by a process called sulphitation, where the crude TNT is treated with aqueous sodium sulfite solution in order to remove less stable isomers of TNT and other undesired reaction products. The rinse water from sulphitation is known as red water and is a significant pollutant and waste product of TNT manufacture.
12902404.creator: ROBLOX

Prized for their ability to slice through viridian steel exoskeletons, the US was determined to find a substitute for the pure diamond required for the manufacture of the Beta models. People get jealous cuz we always stay together / yeah baby / I guess they really want a love like yours and mine / together forever / I never thought that I could ever be this happy" 
Yeah I know these are the lyrics to "Two of Heart" and not "Ace of Hearts"... but is there a good song called "Ace of Hearts"? Not one that I've heard of. I challenge you to write your own and PM it to me.

46360870.name: Ice Axe

46363235.description: "Abe didn't say a word.  He made straight for his journal and and wrote down a single sentence. One that would radically alter the course of his life, and bring a fledgeling nation to the brink of collapse.  I hearby resolve to kill every vampire in America."
46363235.creator: ROBLOX

46363291.name: For the Ages: George Washington
46363291.description: "To be prepared for War is one of the most effectual means of preserving peace."

51243538.description: This mummy will make you want your mommy!
51243538.creator: ROBLOX

51244401.name: Peacock Feathered Adventurer
51244401.description: He went wherever his hat took him. Most of the time, that was a good thing.  But the peacock adventurer... not so good for the peacocks....
51244401.creator: ROBLOX

51244479.name: Rhino Trooper
51244479.description: The noble rhino troopers set up sting operations to catch poachers.  Are you brave enough to join them?
51244479.creator: ROBLOX

51244495.name: Rogue Pilot
51244495.description: You've disobeyed your commanding officer and went on a humanitarian mission for the president.  You've just gone rogue!
51244495.creator: ROBLOX

51244757.name: Sabretooth Leader
51244757.description: His false teeth contain the venom of 1000 snakes. The only way to survive is to be a honeybadger!
51244757.creator: ROBLOX

51244770.name: Sandy Desert Warrior
51244770.description: The desert is a dangerous place if you don't know how to navigate the shifting sands.
51244770.creator: ROBLOX

51245193.name: Great White Warrior
51245193.description: Like the Great White Shark, he is one of the deadliest foes you will ever encounter, on the sea or on land!
51245193.creator: ROBLOX

51245220.name: Captain Silly
51245220.description: Thar be silly pirates in these waters.  Beware Captain Silly and his oversized pirate hat.
51245220.creator: ROBLOX

51245277.name: Violet Sneaking Slytherer
51245277.description: Sneaking and slithering, you strike before anyone notices.
51245277.creator: ROBLOX

51245297.name: Space Biker
51245297.description: You should be safe - even in space!
51245297.creator: ROBLOX

51245692.name: King of New Calclica
51245692.description: You rule the new world with an iron fist.
51245692.creator: ROBLOX

51245710.name: Space Mercenary
51245710.description: He wanders from planet to planet, looking for trouble.
51245710.creator: ROBLOX

51245739.name: Steampunk Lincoln
51245739.description: If Lincoln were steampunk, and not a vampire hunter, he might look something like this.
51245739.creator: ROBLOX

51245765.name: Steampunk Skull
51245765.description: The wheels of your mind are turning. Literally.
51245765.creator: ROBLOX

51245785.name: Supreme Ruler
51245785.description: You do not choose the crown, it chooses you.
51245785.creator: ROBLOX

51245837.name: Tic Toc Top
51245837.description: This hat has a clock on the right side of it. Tic Toc on the clock, but the party don't stop!
51245837.creator: ROBLOX

51245885.name: Ultraviolet Pilot
51245885.description: He's around when your plane is going down.  He'll see it through and is always true!
51245885.creator: ROBLOX

51245910.name: Aquatic Robotic
51245910.description: All that saltwater would destroy most robots, but not aquatic robotic!
51245910.creator: ROBLOX

51245952.name: Dark Knight of the 9th Kingdom
51245952.description: It is a truth universally acknowledged that the a Knight from the sinister 9th Kingdom must be in want of a knife.
51245952.creator: ROBLOX

51245982.name: Astomel's Helmet
51245982.description: Astomel fought strongly to protect the weak. This pleased the gods and they rewarded him with this winged helmet, so that he might someday see them in their dwellings.
51245982.creator: ROBLOX

51302649.name: Knights of the Splintered Sky: Sword and Shield
51302649.description: The Knights of the Splintered Sky have descended to ROBLOX to help the Knights of Redcliff defeat the evil Zombies.  Are you brave enough to join them?
51302649.creator: ROBLOX

51346271.name: Bamboo Dart Blowgun
51346271.description: From the infamous Shadow Ninjas of Robloxia comes this blowgun capable of firing 3 deadly darts at insane speeds.
51346271.creator: ROBLOX

51346336.name: Ninja Sai
51346336.description: The primary melee weapon of the Shadow Ninjas, the Sai, comes in two pieces to wreak its opponents. With its lightness and speed it also allows the wearing Ninja the ability to move faster.
51346336.creator: ROBLOX

51346471.name: Twin Kodachi
51346471.description: From the Asuna Samurais comes this twin Kodachi. With its lightness and speed, the Kodachi is deadly in the hands of any true Samurai warrior. Give them two and see them cut through their opponents as if they were made of paper.
51346471.creator: ROBLOX

51347716.name: Noble RedCliff Eagle
51347716.description: To aid in the grand war against the Korbloxian Zombies, the faithful companion of the Knights of RedCliff follows its Master to the battlefield. With the strength of the Zombies ever increasing, the Eagle of RedCliff's help is definitely necessary for any and every Knight.
51347716.creator: ROBLOX

51352983.name: Umadbro?
51352983.description: Umad that you don't have this tie?
51352983.creator: ROBLOX

51352999.name: Epic Face Tie
51352999.description: You're epic and you've got the tie to prove it!
51352999.creator: ROBLOX

51353061.name: Art Tie
51353061.description: People pay millions of dollars for paintings like this....the world is crazy!
51353061.creator: ROBLOX

51353073.name: Duke of Rustington
51353073.description: Being the Duke of Rustington is not the honor that the title "Duke" might imply....
51353073.creator: ROBLOX

51353085.name: Game Over
51353085.description: How many lives do you have left? 0 more lives. GAME OVER!
51353085.creator: ROBLOX

51353099.name: Dragon Slayer Hood
51353099.description: You have slayed the dragon, and now wear his protective skin everywhere, in case his dragon family comes for vengance.
51353099.creator: ROBLOX

51757126.name: Korblox: Spiked Arm Bracer
51757126.description: This pair of spiked arm bracers are predominantly used by the wild Korbloxians for melee combat. Beware of anyone wearing this, as it is quite deadly at close range!
51757126.creator: ROBLOX

51757158.name: Korblox: Tripmine
51757158.description: These ghastly mines were invented by the Korbloxians to trap anyone and everyone brave enough to ever venture out into the wilds.
51757158.creator: ROBLOX

51757162.name: Korblox: Berserker's Claymore
51757162.description:
Crafted using their corrupted magic, this claymore is as deadly as it is heavy. Handed down from generation to generation to the mightiest Korbloxian warriors, this legendary weapon was once wielded by Canavus himself. 

With its ability to double its strength in the blink of an eye, this weapon outmatches almost all weapons at close range. Only the mighty knight Xargas is said to have be able to hold his own against this claymore!
51757162.creator: ROBLOX

51760061.name: Korblox: DeathSpeaker's Zombie Creator
51760061.description: This once powerful wizard dagger, tainted by the DeathSpeaker blood now serves the Korbloxians well! Said to be wielded only by the strongest DeathSpeakers of Korbloxia, the dagger creates a Zombie of its victims and helps its Master do his bidding.
51760061.creator: ROBLOX

52180858.name: Footbag
52180858.description: Have some colorful fun with this colorful footbag! Pull off some cool moves and show it off to your friends! Time to enjoy the summer!
52180858.creator: ROBLOX

52180863.name: Flute
52180863.description: Time to go out enjoy the breeze  and play some soothing music! Watch as you play the flute, nearby Robloxians dancing to your tune!
52180863.creator: ROBLOX

52180871.name: Remote Controlled Monster Truck
52180871.description: The latest in the series, the powerful Monster Truck! Control the truck with the regular movement keys and watch as it breaks top speeds across the board. With enough strength to move objects, at full speed, this Truck is a beast!
52180871.creator: ROBLOX

52180878.name: Ultimate Slide Skateboard
52180878.description: Time to show off as the coolest kid on the block!
52180878.creator: ROBLOX

52454955.name: Emerald Crescent Samurai
52454955.description: All the other samurai are green with envy.
52454955.creator: ROBLOX

52456325.name: Dragon Tamer
52456325.description: His knowledge of dragons was unparalleled.  The egg was abandoned.  What was he supposed to do? Leave it.  Never.  He hand raised the dragon himself and became the world's first dragon tamer.
52456325.creator: ROBLOX

52461245.name: Military Periscope Goggles
52461245.description: The ultimate in underwater (and above!) vision technology.
52461245.creator: ROBLOX

52462233.name: Summer Hat
52462233.description: When I asked for a summer hat, this isn't exactly what I meant! Lol
52462233.creator: ROBLOX

52463255.name: Rainbow Sunglasses
52463255.description: Stay cool in these hot shades!
52463255.creator: ROBLOX

52464382.name: Dino Jaw Crown
52464382.description: You were victorious over a dinosaur!  Awesome! Oh...you got it at the science museum? I guess that's cool too....
52464382.creator: ROBLOX

52487443.name: Scarf 'Do
52487443.description: Stay stylin' with this awesome scarf / hair combo!
52487443.creator: ROBLOX

52488383.name: Alycylone Hunter
52488383.description: Like the brave little toaster, except you know, more deadly. Also it doesn't make toast....
52488383.creator: ROBLOX

52489004.name: Lone Spaceman
52489004.description: Like the lone ranger but with you know...more space! No not literal space - like outerspace! I get the feeling you're being deliberately obtuse...
52489004.creator: ROBLOX

52489477.name: Dangerface: The Hat
52489477.description: He is called Dangerface for a reason.  If you can't see why by looking, you get what you get!
52489477.creator: ROBLOX

52489921.name: Colossal Tides Golem
52489921.description: The ocean is a mightly foe.
52489921.creator: ROBLOX

52490497.name: Horned Menace
52490497.description: He's got horns, and he doesn't mess around.
52490497.creator: ROBLOX

52491335.name: Desert Special Ops
52491335.description: The elite special ops team doesn't accept just anyone.  Only the best, forget the rest.
52491335.creator: ROBLOX

52492417.name: Korblox King
52492417.description: The typical Korblox King does not reign for long.  The King must fight to keep the position against anyone who dares to challenge him for the kingdom.
52492417.creator: ROBLOX

52493131.name: Fearsome Warrior of the Far Lands
52493131.description: You can run away, but you cannot escape.  The Warrior of the Far Lands will find you.  Better to face him honorably.
52493131.creator: ROBLOX

52497621.name: Puffer Fish
52497621.description: If you startle him, be prepared to face the consequences.
52497621.creator: ROBLOX

52498580.name: Galactic Assasin
52498580.description: The fate of the galaxy hangs in the balance.  One man.  One chance to save the world.  Are you brave enough to answer the call!?!
52498580.creator: ROBLOX

52499442.name: Ramblin' Witch
52499442.description: Wanders the countryside looking for high stakes card games.  I wouldn't play against her, but that's just me.
52499442.creator: ROBLOX

52500238.name: Goblin Prisoner
52500238.description: He is imprisoned in his own mind.  The cruelest kind of imprisonment?  I think so....
52500238.creator: ROBLOX

52501424.name: Teenage Monster
52501424.description: Human teenagers think they know everything.  Teenage monsters are the same, but with sharper teeth.
52501424.creator: ROBLOX

52502129.name: Dare Devil
52502129.description: "I know guys in my hometown that drive by feel and sound."- Evel Knievel
52502129.creator: ROBLOX

52502756.name: Gogglebicorns
52502756.description: It's like you're a dragon that killed two unicorns and took their horns as victory tokens and then put on goggles because you're too cool to walk around with bare eyes.
52502756.creator: ROBLOX

52504099.name: Kitty Monster
52504099.description: Like a real cat - hides in your closet, likes to nom, etc. Only difference is he likes to nom humans!
52504099.creator: ROBLOX

52505168.name: The Eliminator
52505168.description: He eliminates problems... with whatever tools are at his disposal.
52505168.creator: ROBLOX

52505901.name: Metropolitan Party Cyborg
52505901.description: He's in your city, throwin' cyborg parties!
52505901.creator: ROBLOX

52512136.name: The Blind Seer
52512136.description: Blind since birth, technology has allowed him to see more than any other man since the dawn of time.
52512136.creator: ROBLOX

52514294.name: Crimson Fighter
52514294.description: The Crimson awaits... do you dare to face him?!?!
52514294.creator: ROBLOX

52515336.name: Olympian Royalty
52515336.description: Frames your face and makes you look awesome!
52515336.creator: ROBLOX

52539791.name: Paranoia Attack
52539791.description: He's paranoid so you don't have to be.
52539791.creator: ROBLOX

52540425.name: Angry Android
52540425.description: Do you think the red light in his eyes means he's happy? Yeah... me neither.....
52540425.creator: ROBLOX

52542282.name: Futuristic Leader
52542282.description: He believes his hat sees things he doesn't.
52542282.creator: ROBLOX

52542813.name: Star Fighter Pilot
52542813.description: He's on the front lines of the space battle, and he's lovin' it!
52542813.creator: ROBLOX

52550492.name: Platinum and Sapphire Circlet of the Elven King
52550492.description: The Sapphire King rules the Blue Elves...the other kings make fun of him and call his elves Smurfs.  The other kings are jealous of the Sapphire Elves' powers.  The benevolent Sapphire King knows this and ignores their comments.
52550492.creator: ROBLOX

52552283.name: Pyrowizard
52552283.description: Ignites things at will.  Stand back - or face a fire attack!
52552283.creator: ROBLOX

52553970.name: Dragon Guard
52553970.description: Only the bravest are chosen to guard the dragon.  It is a great honor and an even greater responsibility.
52553970.creator: ROBLOX

52555336.name: Flora
52555336.description: "But we love trees, we love the snow, the friends we have, the world we share ... and we find magic everywhere."
52555336.creator: ROBLOX

52556526.name: Captain of the Pikemen
52556526.description: He led the charge, without fear or hesitation
52556526.creator: ROBLOX

52558745.name: Sacred Fighter of the Ninth Wonder
52558745.description: He must protect the secrets of the Ninth Wonder with his life.
52558745.creator: ROBLOX

52564187.name: Black Magic Top Hat
52564187.description: He'll do what you ask...but it will cost you.  No... not money....
52564187.creator: ROBLOX

52625728.name: United States of Rock Guitar
52625728.description: This week, celebrate America in style!  This rockin' guitar plays some sweet tunes!
52625728.creator: ROBLOX

52625733.name: Merica Airwalker
52625733.description: Cuz this is my United States of Whatever....
52625733.creator: ROBLOX

52625744.name: Picnic Basket
52625744.description: Hello pic-i-nic basket!  Activate this picnic basket and get yourself some delicious ROBLOX food!
52625744.creator: ROBLOX

52627419.name: Basketball
52627419.description: Dribble the ball and pass it to your friends!
52627419.creator: ROBLOX

52926818.name: Common Superhero
52926818.description: If there is a will, there is a superhero!
52926818.creator: ROBLOX

52938493.name: Admiral's Cutlass - A Walmart Exclusive!
52938493.description: Get this for free when you redeem a Walmart gamecard in June 2011!  It is said that the admiral rose quickly throught the ranks because of his superior swordsmanship.  But perhaps it was the sword itself?
52938493.creator: ROBLOX

53036012.name: Android Deputy
53036012.description: I shot the sherriff.  But I did not shoot the android deputy!  Plus shooting a robot? Doesn't much brain power to know that's ineffective.  Just throw some water on their circuits.  Duh!
53036012.creator: ROBLOX

53037068.name: Scientific Eyeware
53037068.description: People will stare when you wear your scientific eyeware, but don't dismay!  Tell them it's for science and be on your way!
53037068.creator: ROBLOX

53037798.name: Steampunk Elephant
53037798.description: They've got Steampunk everything else so why not an elephant.
53037798.creator: ROBLOX

53039427.name: Pretty Pretty Princess
53039427.description: You're the fairest of them all!
53039427.creator: ROBLOX

53040003.name: Paperball Tiara
53040003.description: Here she is.... Miss America....no wait. Ms. Paperball America...that's not right either.  Just take the crown.
53040003.creator: ROBLOX

53041013.name: Grand Master Knight
53041013.description: His sword swings brave and true.
53041013.creator: ROBLOX

53055197.name: Mystical Techno Sand Walker
53055197.description: The sand can hide all kinds of enemies.  The techno eye lets him see what his own eye cannot.
53055197.creator: ROBLOX

53058072.name: King of the Monster Palace
53058072.description: The king of the Monster Palace is the most fearsome of all the monsters! No one has as many horns and snarls as he.
53058072.creator: ROBLOX

53061135.name: Horned Master of the Dragon Horde
53061135.description: Few are allowed to enter the Dragon Horde's lair.  Even fewer are allowed to leave. Those that do, are forever masters and friends of the world's dragons.
53061135.creator: ROBLOX

53068502.name: Cowl Of Villain
53068502.description: Every game has a villain (okay maybe not scrabble) - this time you're it!
53068502.creator: ROBLOX

53130850.name: Brighteyes's Sparkling Shillelagh
53130850.description: Made with solid oak, and sprinkled with some Brighteyess magic, this sparkling Shillelagh, will help you bend some bones! Watch out, this Shillelagh hits hard!
53130850.creator: ROBLOX

53130867.name: JediTkacheff's DeathStar
53130867.description:
Crafted using futuristic techniques by JediTkacheff this death star is capable of moving and blistering speeds to attack its marked target. Watch out though, as the star is also capable of conjuring a shield around its wielder to protect him from incoming projectiles and do damage to any tresspassers and boost your health.

Press "x" for conjuring the shield!
53130867.creator: ROBLOX

53130887.name: RobloTim's RobloHunk Potion
53130887.description: Want to be the next superstar in town? Then this potion is for you! Brewed by our very own RobloTim, this potion make you into a solid weight lifting champion. Huge muscles, strong arms and giving + 100% health and movement speed! Once transformed you can use other gear to fight or show off!
53130887.creator: ROBLOX

53130896.name: HotThoth's Voodoo Doll
53130896.description: Created in his own image, this cuddly doll is enchanted with some ancient magic. Only given to his special apprentices, this doll uses its magic to help its wielder, by increasing health, increasing movement speed and firing fireballs/ice shards at the wielder's enemies
53130896.creator: ROBLOX

53420165.name: Zeppelin Top Hat
53420165.description: It's hard for zeppelin enthusiast to find an appropriate hat. As zeppelin enthusiasts ourselves, we know this. We present you with the Zeppelin Top Hat - because you deserve a hat that reflects your lifestyle.
53420165.creator: ROBLOX

53424137.name: Black Knight Tournament Champion
53424137.description: Each year, new knights enter the tournament, each year the Black Knight remains undefeated.
53424137.creator: ROBLOX

53426023.name: Ye Olde Flat Cap
53426023.description: Ye Old Flat Cap for all of your Renaissance hat needs.  'Tis a fyne cap indeed!
53426023.creator: ROBLOX

53427994.name: The Amazing Roboto!
53427994.description: Watch as the amazing roboto performs death defying stunts!
53427994.creator: ROBLOX

53429817.name: Courageous Warrior King
53429817.description: His bravery is matched only by his generosity towards his loyal subjects.
53429817.creator: ROBLOX

53457749.name: Monster Palace Royal Guard
53457749.description: All the guards at the Monster Palace are dressed in their finest gleaming armor.
53457749.creator: ROBLOX

53459092.name: Mischief Maker
53459092.description: He's just lookin' to start trouble.
53459092.creator: ROBLOX

53460226.name: Opconius: Baron of the Lawfull Rebellion
53460226.description: His unparallelled leadership won the rebels their own kingdom and the freedom to harvest the fruits of their own labor.  Known to those outside the Kingdom as the Land of unlawful rebels, they must work hard to maintain their freedom.
53460226.creator: ROBLOX

53461320.name: Mardi Skull Mask
53461320.description: Should be worn on Tuesdays only...nah j/k.
53461320.creator: ROBLOX

53462296.name: Sapphire Prince of the Future
53462296.description: He relays all battle commands directly to the team from his wireless headset.
53462296.creator: ROBLOX

53466788.name: Flying Meteor
53466788.description: Why is a meteor orbiting your head?  Because you're a star!
53466788.creator: ROBLOX

53469527.name: Optiscope 650
53469527.description: Sir, I've spotted the enemy.  He's at N 53 32' 6.1872", W 9 53' 19.9134".  What are your orders?
53469527.creator: ROBLOX

53524217.name: Lock N Key Necklace
53524217.description: I keep my love locked down...also my neck.
53524217.creator: ROBLOX

53623248.name: Builderman's Hammer of Shimmering Light
53623248.description:
Better to light one small candle  
than to curse the darkness.
53623248.creator: ROBLOX

53623295.name: Njay's Web Blaster
53623295.description: Everyone knows that Njay writes web code like nobody's business, but did you know he also shoots spider webs that stop people from moving and do some serious damage?
53623295.creator: ROBLOX

53623322.name: Sorcus' Sword of Judgement
53623322.description: "Judge a man by his questions rather than by his answers" -Voltaire
53623322.creator: ROBLOX

53623350.name: Telamon's Foe Hammer
53623350.description: For when a ban hammer just doesn't hit hard enough.
53623350.creator: ROBLOX

53898421.name: King Poseidon's Crown
53898421.description: Keepin' the seas calm and carryin' on.... except when you make him angry.  Then you're in for crazy storms.
53898421.creator: ROBLOX

53901180.name: Vaquero Sombrero
53901180.description: Only the baddest vaqueros wore pure silver sombreros.
53901180.creator: ROBLOX

53902776.name: Knight King
53902776.description: In his heart, the King always knew he was meant to be a knight.  He fought bravely among his men and was respected all the more for his prowess on the field of battle.
53902776.creator: ROBLOX

53903944.name: Adventure Girl
53903944.description: For the adventure girl who is always on the go - we present goggles and pigtails! Fashionable and functional!
53903944.creator: ROBLOX

53914346.name: Mystic Cowl
53914346.description: When there is nowhere else to turn, they turn to him.  His dark magic will solve any problem, but it comes at a price.
53914346.creator: ROBLOX

53917288.name: Walrus
53917288.description: I am the eggman.  They are the eggman.  I am the WALRUS!
53917288.creator: ROBLOX

53920070.name: Dancing Strawberry
53920070.description: He likes to get down, but he doesn't like to jam... for obvious reasons.
53920070.creator: ROBLOX

53920804.name: Arachnid Crown
53920804.description: Fear the gaze of his six eyes.  Fear the steps of his eight legs. But most of all fear the bite of his two fangs.
53920804.creator: ROBLOX

54130537.name: Seashell Snare
54130537.description: She sells seashells by the seashore.   But she doesn't mess around.  This shell is a trap that will ensnare any enemies that get too close!
54130537.creator: ROBLOX

54130543.name: Sword Fish
54130543.description: Get it?  Cuz it's a sword...made of fish?
54130543.creator: ROBLOX

54130552.name: Starfish Shooter
54130552.description: Launches a starfish, and it will stick to your target.  Shoot too many starfish and it might obscure your opponent's vision!
54130552.creator: ROBLOX

54130559.name: Poseidon's Quake Trident
54130559.description: Shake the land and sea with Poseidon's Quake Trident!
54130559.creator: ROBLOX

54376950.name: Steel Horned Samurai
54376950.description: The steel horned samurai take orders from no one.
54376950.creator: ROBLOX

54380918.name: Zombie Cat
54380918.description: Zombie cat on your head? You keep strange company.
54380918.creator: ROBLOX

54528375.name: Shady Shades
54528375.description: I like to wear these shades when I'm about to do something shady...like burn holes through things with my eyes....
54528375.creator: ROBLOX

54578891.name: ROBLOX CS Headset
54578891.description: Just like the ones MSE6 wears!  Well all CS really...
54578891.creator: ROBLOX

54582640.name: Headlight Headphones
54582640.description: Do you ever put on some headphones, rock out, and they say "Man, I wish my headphones had lights on them so I could dance around and shine spotlights all over the place?" Yeah, me too!  Problem solved!
54582640.creator: ROBLOX

54583936.name: Monster Sergeant
54583936.description: He keeps the other monsters in line.
54583936.creator: ROBLOX

54585293.name: Mega Awesome Guy
54585293.description: He's not just awesome, he's mega awesome!
54585293.creator: ROBLOX

54586667.name: Water Mage Hood
54586667.description: Some say the mysteries of the sea are unsolvable.  The Water Mage disagrees...
54586667.creator: ROBLOX

54595552.name: Webbed Witch
54595552.description: Part spider, part witch.  Beware the webbed witch.
54595552.creator: ROBLOX

54694311.name: Ruby Encrusted Sword of the Mighty
54694311.description: The Mighty lost his sword many years ago in fierce battle. It is said that he who wields the sword will summon his return and the destruction of all coffee shops.  Yeah - it's a weird legend.
54694311.creator: ROBLOX

54694329.name: Sword of the Summer Sun
54694329.description: The pain of a million sunburns...
54694329.creator: ROBLOX

54694334.name: Vilethorn
54694334.description: Wrap your enemies in the vilest of thorns.
54694334.creator: ROBLOX

54923731.name: Solid Gold Kaiser
54923731.description: If you saw his eyes, it would be the last thing you ever saw.
54923731.creator: ROBLOX

54925475.name: Druid Hood
54925475.description: Deep in the forest, keepin' it magical.
54925475.creator: ROBLOX

54928319.name: Crazy Skull

It was rebuilt in 1965, and renovation of the lagoon, walkways, and a seismic retrofit were completed in early 2009.

60331861.description: Friend and ally of Lord Lucas, the Dark Soldier fought bravely on the frontline of the wars against the cavemen.  The war is over, but he's not done fighting.
60331861.creator: ROBLOX

60357959.name: Knights of the Seventh Sanctum: Sword and Shield
60357959.description: With their duty to stabilize Robloxia, they care not for what is right nor for what is wrong, but for stability. They are dangerous beyond belief and their undead nature strikes fear into the hearts of their enemies
60357959.creator: ROBLOX

60357972.name: Flaming Hedgehog Cannon
60357972.description: Because laser guns are way too predictable...
60357972.creator: ROBLOX

60357989.name: Silly Stilts
60357989.description: You'll earn that scholarship to clown college in no time!
60357989.creator: ROBLOX

60662839.name: Discophones
60662839.description: "No parking, baby.  No parking on the dance floor!"
60662839.creator: ROBLOX

60662904.name: Firin' mai Tie!
60662904.description: Ima firin' mai Tie!  See that's funny because the tie looks like it's on fire.  Maybe it got hit with a laser?  Maybe you just stood too close to the campfire... Wait, why were you wearing a tie at a campfire.  Seems a bit too formal.
60662904.creator: ROBLOX

60662967.name: Green Checkered Bow Tie
60662967.description: Because sometimes neon green is exactly the right color.
60662967.creator: ROBLOX

60674516.name: The Party
60674516.description: You don't go to parties, you are the party!
60674516.creator: ROBLOX

60674606.name: Sinister Skull Mask
60674606.description: Up to no good with a skull mask under my hood.
60674606.creator: ROBLOX

60674654.name: Fire Fighter
60674654.description: I am fire's fighter. I speak for the flames.
60674654.creator: ROBLOX

60674719.name: Dark Wolf
60674719.description: I tend to think of myself as a one-man wolf pack.
60674719.creator: ROBLOX

60678464.name: Metal Guitar of Awesomeness
60678464.description: You'll have all your friends dancing when you play the Metal Guitar of Awesomeness.  Get the Metal Guitar of Awesomeness for free when you purchase a ROBLOX Card at Walmart during the month of September..
60678464.creator: ROBLOX

60888200.name: DarkAge Ninjas: SunFire Scroll
60888200.description: Use the power of the scroll, to unleash a torrent of sunfire blast around you!
60888200.creator: ROBLOX

60888284.name: DarkAge Ninjas: Dual Kamas
60888284.description: Fast and Elegant. Strike at the hearts of your enemies or spin like the hurricane destroying anything and everything in your path!
60888284.creator: ROBLOX

60888308.name: DarkAge Ninjas: Combat Potion
60888308.description:
The DarkAge Ninjas are masters of hand to hand combat that none but the fiercest of warriors can handle. 

Drink this potion to increase your vitality to two fold, and to learn to spin kick, flash kick and charge kick in the face, decimating anyone who tries to fight you.
60888308.creator: ROBLOX

61219772.name: Original DriveBlox VIP
61219772.description:
This shirt will still allow VIP access within DriveBlox games.

It will no longer be sold as it has now been replaced by the new Game Pass system.
61219772.creator: nfsboy

61454151.name: Apeeling Shades
61454151.description: You'll look stylish in these apeeling shades!  Don't peel them though.
61454151.creator: ROBLOX

61457692.name: Tropical Fishy
61457692.description: You guys picked up weird souvenirs from your summer vacation.
61457692.creator: ROBLOX

61458403.name: Palm Tree Sunglasses
61458403.description: This is taking the island lifestyle a bit too far I think.
61458403.creator: ROBLOX

61459592.name: Ne'Kotikoz Incarnate
61459592.description: Trade places with your intergalactic friend (or perhaps fiend?) and shoot fireballs at your enemies.
61459592.creator: ROBLOX

61459678.name: Ne'Kotikoz Phaser
61459678.description: The Ne'Kotikoz will ask you to move politely, then they'll pull out the Phasers.  Trust me, you don't want them to pull out the Phasers.
61459678.creator: ROBLOX

61459706.name: Staff of Shifting Polarity
61459706.description: When you use the Staff of Shifting Polarity, all near by players are pulled to the nearest object.  This force is unstoppable!
61459706.creator: ROBLOX

61459718.name: The Tormentor's Axe
61459718.description: Only the very best escape the hot steel of the Tormentor's Axe!
61459718.creator: ROBLOX

61460764.name: Slim Slimy Crab
61460764.description: Those legs don't look like good eatin'
61460764.creator: ROBLOX

61686118.name: Electrochapeau Malifisant
61686118.description: Le electrochapeau malifisant est ici.  Qu'allons nous-faire?
61686118.creator: ROBLOX

61687778.name: Gorilla Mask
61687778.description: You'll go ape for this wild gorilla mask!
61687778.creator: ROBLOX

61769697.name: Octopus's Garden
61769697.description: Who knew that the garden was your head?
61769697.creator: ROBLOX

61781295.name: Ravegreen[5]
61781295.description: 1st coloured pair of rave pants of the 5th series
61781295.creator: Eggnivia

61847146.name: Halloween 2011 Paintball Cap
61847146.description: This at least proves that you know how to join a winning team and idle in their server while they carry you. Congrats.
61847146.creator: ROBLOX

61848064.name: Halloween 2011 Paintball MVP Trophy
61848064.description: At least for a time and in a place, you were the fastest trigger in the Dunfort.
61848064.creator: ROBLOX

61889430.name: Order of the Golden Crest
61889430.description: The king gives this hat to only the bravest soldiers.  It is a matter of honor to wear the hat at all times.  If at any time a member of the Order of the Golden Crest is killed in battle - the helmet is buried with him in the Royal Cemetary.
61889430.creator: ROBLOX

61895706.name: Seeking Sea King
61895706.description: He seeks she who sells seashells by the seashore.  He's tired of his friends being stolen and sold and is ready to do something about it!
61895706.creator: ROBLOX

61899632.name: Buffalo Tooth Necklace
61899632.description: Stylish and practical! The teeth double as primative tools!
61899632.creator: ROBLOX

61901074.name: Abraham Dusek
61901074.description: 1 part Dusek + 1 part Lincoln = 100% speed + 100% freedom = 200% awesome!
61901074.creator: ROBLOX

61902344.name: Golden Ancient
61902344.description: A relic from a soul long since gone...
61902344.creator: ROBLOX

61903103.name: The Darkest Gladiator
61903103.description: He fought the lion... and won!
61903103.creator: ROBLOX

61904706.name: Oceanic Guard Helmet
61904706.description: The Oceanic Guard are an elite squad of men chosen to protect the Prince of the Seas.
61904706.creator: ROBLOX

61905782.name: Skull Cookie Sunglasses
61905782.description: Delicious sugar cookies baked in the shape of cute little skulls and then frosted with chocolate and vanilla icing. Mmmmm.
61905782.creator: ROBLOX

61906732.name: Serpent Sovereign
61906732.description: Obey his forked tongue, or face the consequences. Get this exclusive item when you redeem a Roblox card from Woolworths AU in June 2021.
61906732.creator: ROBLOX

61907531.name: Tiny Top Hat for A Regular Head
61907531.description: High fashion isn't for everyone, but it works for you.
61907531.creator: ROBLOX

61916108.name: Orb Crystal Launcher
61916108.description: Launch your crystals quickly for instant damage. Charge it for a bit and then launch?  Your foe is in a world of trouble.
61916108.creator: ROBLOX

61916132.name: ROBLOXIAN Healing Orb
61916132.description: Heal yourself with this glowing green orb.  No need to heal right now?  Drop healing orbs around a game and pick them up as needed. Why green?  Everyone knows that green is the color of healing...duh.
61916132.creator: ROBLOX

61916137.name: Chameleon Potion
61916137.description: No it's not a karma chameleon - and thank goodness for that!  This will transform your appearance to be like whatever you click.  Now you see me... now you think I'm a grey baseboard.
61916137.creator: ROBLOX

61963621.name: Telamax XR71 Shoulder Cannon
61963621.description: The Telemax XR71 Shoulder Cannon is a vital piece in every soldier's arsenal.  Shoot your enemies and revitalize yourself!
61963621.creator: ROBLOX

62129759.name: Stones of History
62129759.description: Can you imagine wearing a hat made of stone?  Yeah me neither.... and I don't want to.
62129759.creator: ROBLOX

62130183.name: Plume Albidus
62130183.description: Death is light as a feather.
62130183.creator: ROBLOX

62131438.name: Woodlands Hood
62131438.description: Because it's cold in the woods. Everyone knows that.
62131438.creator: ROBLOX

62133625.name: Merfolk Minion
62133625.description: Thinking about throwing that oil down a drain?  Think again.
62133625.creator: ROBLOX

62134823.name: Gadgetron 2700
62134823.description: Whatever you need, Gadgetron's got you covered.  Unless you need a cookie.  There is no room in Gadgetron for cookies.  Cookies are not gadgets.
62134823.creator: ROBLOX

62136561.name: Bronze Circle Knight
62136561.description: It is said that the town's eldest blacksmith was part wizard, and that's how he could affix liquid bronze to the Bronze Circle Knight's Helmets, but no one knows for sure.
62136561.creator: ROBLOX

62139501.name: Brighteyes' Summer Vacation Leftovers
62139501.description: Summer's over, but Brighteyes still has some summer hats.  Who doesn't love leftovers? Interrupting starfish for the win!
62139501.creator: ROBLOX

62141734.name: Feathered Bloxxing Machine
62141734.description: The inventor of this robot thought it would be funny to give his bloxxing robot some silly feathers. He didn't count on his creation not getting the joke.
62141734.creator: ROBLOX

62147392.name: Muddy Mask
62147392.description: It's a dirty job, but somebody has to do it.
62147392.creator: ROBLOX

62150694.name: Winged Helm of the Northern Brothers
62150694.description: They move so fast it feels like they're flying.
62150694.creator: ROBLOX

62152671.name: Poison Horns
62152671.description: Probably not a smart idea to make see through compartments for the poison in your hat.
62152671.creator: ROBLOX

62229189.name: Shortsighted Shapeshifter
62229189.description: Key advice to shapeshifters - don't forget to take off your hat!
62229189.creator: ROBLOX

62232358.name: Forest Warrior of the Jungly Woods
62232358.description: He's hidin' in a tree - waiting to ambush you.
62232358.creator: ROBLOX

62233675.name: Sarge's Helmet
62233675.description: If anybody can do it - it's Sarge.
62233675.creator: ROBLOX

62235416.name: Lord Lucas: Vanquisher of Cavemen
62235416.description: The people of ROBLOX had been terrorized by cavemen for many years.  Finally - Lord Lucas had enough!  He rallied the ROBLOXIAN troops and defeated the cavemen with painfully precise sword swipes and gantt charts.
62235416.creator: ROBLOX

62238118.name: Winged Monster
62238118.description: Is that a monster on your head or did you get a bad hair cut?
62238118.creator: ROBLOX

62242344.name: Checkered Neon Green Fedora
62242344.description: People notice a man in a neon green fedora.  Believe me they do.
62242344.creator: ROBLOX

62243290.name: Sheriff Tarabyte
62243290.description: There's a new sheriff in town... okay it's actually the same sheriff as usual....
62243290.creator: ROBLOX

62245191.name: Prince of the Gilded Feather
62245191.description: Death is as light as a feather, duty heavier than a mountain
62245191.creator: ROBLOX

62248391.name: Rollo the Walker
62248391.description: So named, because no horse was big enough to carry him.
62248391.creator: ROBLOX

62250286.name: Autumn Brimmed Beanie
62250286.description: You want to look cool but not be cold?  Here ya go!
62250286.creator: ROBLOX

62250917.name: Desert Trooper
62250917.description: Doing what has to be done.  Everyday.
62250917.creator: ROBLOX

62252414.name: Alchemist's Apprentice
62252414.description: The secret to making gold? He'll never tell... probably because he doesn't know it yet.
62252414.creator: ROBLOX

62253088.name: The Duke of Death
62253088.description: It's not a nickname he earned by keeping people alive.
62253088.creator: ROBLOX

62332732.name: Sheriff Wilson
62332732.description: ROBLOX is full of cowboys.  Sheriff Wilson keeps them in line (and testing their code on the test site).
62332732.creator: ROBLOX

62350846.name: Chief Guardsman Spear
62350846.description: Charge directly at your opponent or take them by surprise with a sideswipe attack.
62350846.creator: ROBLOX

62350856.name: Ghostfire Dagger
62350856.description: Does tremendous damage. If you KO your opponent, you'll steal his extra health.
62350856.creator: ROBLOX

62350867.name: Outrageous Sword
62350867.description: Fear will turn your enemies hearts to ice.  The sword will turn all of them to gold.
62350867.creator: ROBLOX

62350883.name: Sword of Ancalagon
62350883.description: More than a mere sword, this amazing tool shoots Ancalagon's own Dragon Fire at anyone in the area.
62350883.creator: ROBLOX

62673504.name: Dark Age Ninja Swordpack
62673504.description: The Darkest Age is still to come....
62673504.creator: ROBLOX

62676917.name: Friendly Cyclops
62676917.description: He's tired of the angry cyclopes myths.  Show people the friendly side of cyclopes with this cap!
62676917.creator: ROBLOX

62678172.name: Shoulder Length Blonde Hair
62678172.description: Keep it stylish with this blonde hair!
62678172.creator: ROBLOX

62679779.name: A Dark Omen
62679779.description: Black birds never mean good things... this bird is no different.
62679779.creator: ROBLOX

62682888.name: Metal Cthulhu Minion
62682888.description: Cthulhu crafted his metal minions in his own image. Once you've seen his minion - it's too late.
62682888.creator: ROBLOX

62683983.name: Fuligin Monk
62683983.description: The Fuligin Monks are an ancient order. They never take off their masks and are known for watching silently from their shadowy alcoves.
62683983.creator: ROBLOX

62684484.name: Lord of the Skeletons
62684484.description: He intends to lead the skeletons to victory over the other undead tribes (vampires, zombies, and mummies).
62684484.creator: ROBLOX

62685648.name: Mighty Minotaur
62685648.description: The mighty minotaur is angry!!  Raig minotaur!
62685648.creator: ROBLOX

62687087.name: Slick Thorn- The Hungry Dragon
62687087.description: My, what big horns you have!  The better to maim.... un I mean uh hug you with?  Okay... I'm going to eat you.
62687087.creator: ROBLOX

62689067.name: Dark Mystic
62689067.description: The darkest magic protects his dual power orbs.  If you can capture one of them, he is your slave forever.
62689067.creator: ROBLOX

62690529.name: Thick Rimmed Glasses 3.0
62690529.description: These stylish glasses fit our latest faces (those included with the man or woman package)!
62690529.creator: ROBLOX

62692030.name: Johnny Brown Hair
62692030.description: Johnny Brown Hair wasn't the best mafia name ever, but it would have to do.
62692030.creator: ROBLOX

62692525.name: Guarded King
62692525.description: His castle and his mind are guarded like a fortress.
62692525.creator: ROBLOX

62718076.name: Emperor of the Three Thrones
62718076.description: He is the emperor of all that shines under the moon, sun, and stars.  Anything else is up for grabs.
62718076.creator: ROBLOX

62718352.name: Crimsonwrath, Duke of Danger
62718352.description: Lesser men quake upon sighting the Crimsonwrath.  Lesser men are reduced to tears by the mere thought of the Duke of Danger.
62718352.creator: ROBLOX

62718789.name: Dark Dragon Lord
62718789.description: Dealing with a dragon lord is a fearful prospect for even the bravest of men.
62718789.creator: ROBLOX

62719170.name: Frivolous Freddy
62719170.description: His hat says more than he ever could.
62719170.creator: ROBLOX

62719569.name: Extreme Brown Hair
62719569.description: His life is so exciting that his hair is constantly on edge!
62719569.creator: ROBLOX

62720062.name: Azurewrath: Lord of the Frost
62720062.description: As the void expands, so does his empire....and hat collection.
62720062.creator: ROBLOX

62720331.name: Harbinger of the Neverending Winter
62720331.description: Yeah - it's going to be cold and coats are going to be the new currency.  Hope you stocked up!
62720331.creator: ROBLOX

62721575.name: Ivory Lion
62721575.description: I was not the lion, but it fell to me to give the lion's roar.
62721575.creator: ROBLOX

62722868.name: Phoenix Mask
62722868.description: The Phoenix shall rise again... and again... without end.
62722868.creator: ROBLOX

62726620.name: 2nd Tour Bombardier
62726620.description: This bombardier has seen it all. Nothing says steely nerves like coming back for more aerial risk-taking action. Bombs away!
62726620.creator: ROBLOX

62729995.name: Crazed Viking
62729995.description: They say that if you ever see his face, you'll be crazy too.
62729995.creator: ROBLOX

62732345.name: Opened The Pendant Gift
62732345.description: Let the lamp affix its beam. The only emperor is the emperor of I-scream. Inside you find... Darkseed: The Pendant!
62732345.creator: ROBLOX

62738208.name: Opened Gift of the Sixth Undead
62738208.description: "Why would you like about anything at all?" ... Inside you find... Vlad the Impaler, VI!
62738208.creator: ROBLOX

62741256.name: Jade Horned Warrior
62741256.description: In the mystic lands, you can never be too careful.
62741256.creator: ROBLOX

62741766.name: Angry Spikes
62741766.description: It's not a hat happy people wear.
62741766.creator: ROBLOX

62743701.name: Stylish Brown Hair
62743701.description: Can't go wrong with a part in the middle.
62743701.creator: ROBLOX

62745593.name: Trader's Cap
62745593.description: Is he a trader or a traitor?  Only one way to find out!  Okay...there are probably several.
62745593.creator: ROBLOX

62745990.name: Honey Blonde Ponytail
62745990.description: I've never seen a sweeter hairstyle.
62745990.creator: ROBLOX

62746419.name: Angry Battle Dwarf
62746419.description: Using his righteous fury to defeat his foes!
62746419.creator: ROBLOX

62803165.name: Trick or Treat Bag 2011
62803165.description: Click this gear and receive a trick or a treat.  Which will it be?  You don't know until it happens!
62803165.creator: ROBLOX

62803173.name: Jack O' Splosion
62803173.description: Oh someone left a jack o lantern for me.... how nice! Oh wait, why is it smoking?  Now that you mention it, his expression is a little menacing.... BOOM! Rut Roh.
62803173.creator: ROBLOX

62809243.name: Outrageous Board with a Nail in It
62809243.description: Did they? That outrageous board with a nail in it may have defeated us. But the humans won't stop there. They'll make bigger boards and bigger nails, and soon, they will make a board with a nail so big, it will destroy them all!
62809243.creator: ROBLOX

62827106.name: Death's Trident: A Walmart Exclusive Item
62827106.description: Charge your enemies with a weapon that's sure to be a hit.  A deadly hit.
62827106.creator: ROBLOX

62827121.name: Wand of the Evil Eye: A Gamestop Exclusive
62827121.description: The evil eye sees all.  It will take your enemies to a place where they cannot see.
62827121.creator: ROBLOX

63043890.name: Purple Sparkle Time Fedora
63043890.description: I like to eat pie in my Sparkle Time Fedora!
63043890.creator: ROBLOX

63083988.name: Opened Obvious Gift is Obvious
63083988.description: Or is it? Inside you find... a Halloween Stage Prop!
63083988.creator: ROBLOX

63084430.name: Opened Cursed Gift of the Full Moon
63084430.description: "Another legend claims that we descended from wolves  and that the wolves are our brothers still" Inside you find... The Leader of the Pack!
63084430.creator: ROBLOX

63088628.name: Opened Cursed Gift of Ramses II
63088628.description: Heavy is the head that wears the crown. Inside you find... Ramses II!
63088628.creator: ROBLOX

63090935.name: Opened Kitchewitch Gift
63090935.description: The Cauldron of Tomorrow, Today! Inside you find... a Poisoned Apple!
63090935.creator: ROBLOX

63091671.name: The Thinker's Gift
63091671.description: Great minds taste alike. Inside you find... Dedrick Edmond Darcy, V.
63091671.creator: ROBLOX

63233124.name: Opened Preeesssennnt
63233124.description: Uhhhhzmmmmuhhuuhhmmzzzhhaaahhhh! Inside you find... Zachary Elloit Dencourt, III
63233124.creator: ROBLOX

63234463.name: Opened Gift of the Three Witches
63234463.description: "Double, double toil and trouble; / Fire burn, and caldron bubble.  / Fillet of a fenny snake, / In the caldron boil and bake; / Eye of newt, and toe of frog, / Wool of bat, and tongue of dog" Inside you find... A Newt Head!
63234463.creator: ROBLOX

63235884.name: Opened Surly Gift of Sorcus
63235884.description: "I don't ever want to feel, like I did that day" Inside you find... Troll Faic!
63235884.creator: ROBLOX

63236375.name: Opened Gift of the Dominator
63236375.description: This gift contains 1 of 3 things: A Dominus, A Domino Crown, or a bunch of icky spiders. Inside you find... the Dominus Messor!
63236375.creator: ROBLOX

63237842.name: Halloween Stage Prop
63237842.description: What kind of musical did you say you were in again? This item came out of the "Opened Obvious Gift is Obvious".
63237842.creator: ROBLOX

63239668.name: Bat Tie
63239668.description: It will drive you bat-tie....get it?  This came out of the Stylized Gift of Chrioptera on October 13th, 2011.
63239668.creator: ROBLOX

63240558.name: Vlad the Impaler, VI
63240558.description: Lil Jon, he always tells the truth - This hat came out of the Gift of the Sixth Undead on October 13th, 2011.
63240558.creator: ROBLOX

63241364.name: Darkseed: The Pendant
63241364.description: Emperor of Ice Cream has nothin' on me.  This hat came out of The Pendant Gift on October 13th, 2011.
63241364.creator: ROBLOX

63245697.name: Sorcerer's Top Hat
63245697.description: Making elixirs is no excuse for dressing like a slob. Keep it classy with the Sorcerer's Top Hat.
63245697.creator: ROBLOX

63247316.name: Golden Aviators
63247316.description:
He's ready to fly in style.  Or at least protect his eyes from lasting damage in style...

These are designed to work best with our latest faces (the faces that come with the Man and Woman packages) http://www.roblox.com/Woman-item?id=86499905 http://www.roblox.com/Man-item?id=86500185
63247316.creator: ROBLOX

63248235.name: Turkey Feather Headdress
63248235.description: Just in time for Thanksgiving - a stylish Turkey Feather Headdress!
63248235.creator: ROBLOX

63249793.name: Woodland Sprite
63249793.description: It's always a great day for a walk in the woods in this hat!
63249793.creator: ROBLOX

63253676.name: Skeleboard
63253676.description: It maybe made of bones but its rock solid! So watch out!
63253676.creator: ROBLOX

63253701.name: Skelefriend
63253701.description: They see him swirlin', They hatin'
63253701.creator: ROBLOX

63253706.name: Fiery Bone Trap
63253706.description: Spread these around to ambush your opponents! Trapped into these bone traps they will be decimated by wild fire!
63253706.creator: ROBLOX

63253718.name: Bone Crusher - Mace and Shield
63253718.description: From crushing joints, to running faster to being stronger to spinning like a tornado, this one has got it all. Use "q" to bring out the shield to protect you from projectiles and tap "w" twice and left click to spin like a blistering hurricane!
63253718.creator: ROBLOX

63641134.name: Newt Head
63641134.description: "She turned me into a newt, she did!"
63641134.creator: ROBLOX

63641685.name: Night Shades
63641685.description: Why do you need sunglasses at night?
63641685.creator: ROBLOX

63642258.name: Stylish Sailor
63642258.description: "They said, 'Come sail away, come sail away, come sail away with me lads /Come sail away, come sail away, come sail away with me'"
63642258.creator: ROBLOX

63642669.name: Prince of the Seas
63642669.description: He rules seashells under the sea shore.
63642669.creator: ROBLOX

63643117.name: Burger Bro
63643117.description: Hey bro, I heard you like burgers, so I made you a double burger so you can eat a burger while you eat a burger.
63643117.creator: ROBLOX

63643732.name: Purple Pigtails
63643732.description: How many purple pigtails would a pelican pull if a pelican could pull purple pigtails?
63643732.creator: ROBLOX

63646305.name: Bacon Tie
63646305.description: Because sometimes you just need a tie made out of ham products.  I can't imagine when that time is, but I'm sure there is a time.
63646305.creator: ROBLOX

63646914.name: Ruffy McRufferton
63646914.description: Everyone's favorite second tier theme park dog is here!  Let's all pull his tail and photobomb his pictures!
63646914.creator: ROBLOX
