87262358.description: The back of this stylish stetson has a stylish skull and crossbones.
87262358.creator: ROBLOX

87262381.name: Eccentric Dark Wizard
87262381.description: His story is as quizzical as his hat.
87262381.creator: ROBLOX

87262405.name: Sea Farin' Zombie
87262405.description: Aye these waters be mighty full o' fish but not a brain for miles....
87262405.creator: ROBLOX

87262534.name: Overseer General
87262534.description: The darkness gathers around him, but he can always see what lies ahead.
87262534.creator: ROBLOX

87361508.name: Chimera
87361508.description: This chimera attacks on command  performing one of three attacks  shooting fireballs, shooting poison, or biting. It does some serious damage with 30-60 damage dealt per attack.
87361508.creator: ROBLOX

87361662.name: Ice Breaker
87361662.description: First he makes it - then he breaks it!  Freeze your enemies, then destroy them while they're stuck in your icy trap.  Does an astounding 14 damage per hit.
87361662.creator: ROBLOX

87361806.name: Meteor Staff
87361806.description: Let the fires and stones of the sky rain down upon all who dare defy you.  If your opponent gets hit by one of the meteors you summon, he will meet a swift end.  Only you are protected from the shower of debris that will rain down when you summon it.
87361806.creator: ROBLOX

87361995.name: Chaos Master's Wing Slasher
87361995.description: Man may not fly in your presence.  Any person with wings will have them slashed by this sword and fall to their peril.  As for your enemies on the ground, they'll have a tough time escaping this swords speedy 24 damage hit.
87361995.creator: ROBLOX

88143060.name: Troll Pet
88143060.description: Use to annoy your friends and enemies alike.
88143060.creator: ROBLOX

88143074.name: Poison Picnic
88143074.description: This green cake with a skull on it is irresistible.  Does 60 damage to any opponent who picks it up.  Why would they pick it up you say?  Because they have no other choice.
88143074.creator: ROBLOX

88143093.name: Pigs Boson Collider
88143093.description: Utilizing the Large Hilarity Collider, researchers created the conditions immediately after the Big Chuckle and discovered the emergence of the Pigs Boson, the fundamental particle of funny that will destroy your target for hilarity.
88143093.creator: ROBLOX

88143166.name: Vaulting Pole
88143166.description: Victory is only one jump away.
88143166.creator: ROBLOX

88146486.name: First Class Fencing Sword
88146486.description: Fence your way to a gold medal with this first class sword.
88146486.creator: ROBLOX

88146497.name: Clown Bomb
88146497.description: Your enemies will explode with laughter.  Okay maybe they'll just laugh a lot.
88146497.creator: ROBLOX

88776193.name: Furnace Face
88776193.description: The heat of his words could burn the beard off your face.
88776193.creator: ROBLOX

88776765.name: Masked Elven Underling
88776765.description: Soon he will be able to remove the mask - but until then he shall not show his face.
88776765.creator: ROBLOX

88777383.name: Light Sentry
88777383.description: It's not easy to hide from the light when this guy's looking for you.
88777383.creator: ROBLOX

88777726.name: Awakened Golem
88777726.description: He's been awakened from his slumber of a thousand years.  Strangely, he does not look happy to see you.
88777726.creator: ROBLOX

88778238.name: Copper Helmed Guard of Dasypodidae
88778238.description: Their helms imitate the shells of those they protect.
88778238.creator: ROBLOX

88778587.name: Blockthorn
88778587.description: The mightly Blockthorn battles on.  He is far from his people but they are never far from his thoughts.
88778587.creator: ROBLOX

88779033.name: Countess of The Wellspring
88779033.description: In a land with no water, the Countess of the Well Spring is a Queen!
88779033.creator: ROBLOX

88779405.name: The Red Dread
88779405.description: If you never see his face, consider yourself lucky.   If you see it and survive, consider it a miracle.
88779405.creator: ROBLOX

88779931.name: 4-3y3s
88779931.description: Just don't call him four eyes.
88779931.creator: ROBLOX

88780485.name: Hood Of Divine Foresight
88780485.description: If you knew what was going to happen, and you could change it, would you?
88780485.creator: ROBLOX

88781004.name: Stonejaw the Terrifying
88781004.description: There's a reason they don't call him Stonejaw the Cuddly.
88781004.creator: ROBLOX

88782502.name: Guardian of the Temple of Light
88782502.description: The truth of the temple burns brighter than all things, but it cannot protect itself.
88782502.creator: ROBLOX

88885069.name: Lord of the Federation
88885069.description: The Wars of Reunification are complete. The Federation is whole once more. All of creation is yours.
88885069.creator: ROBLOX

88885268.name: Discus 2012
88885268.description: Throw this discus far enough and you'll get an explosive reward.
88885268.creator: ROBLOX

88885481.name: Military Dress Sword
88885481.description: Sword of honor, sword of might, strike the right foe tonight.  This sword slashes and lunges.  For a special attack press 'W' twice before striking.
88885481.creator: ROBLOX

88885497.name: S-79 Speed Stunter
88885497.description: This explosive creates a 10-second poisonous cloud with a 20-foot radius, slowing affected players' movements for up to ten seconds and doing 10 damage per second if you get caught in the cloud.
88885497.creator: ROBLOX

88885506.name: Military Spy Satellite
88885506.description: Use this spy satellite to spy on your enemies, regardless of where they are on the map.  Gives you a birds-eye-view of the map. Click on a location to zoom in and see what's going on there. Press x to leave the satellite view.
88885506.creator: ROBLOX

88885524.name: Stun Grenade
88885524.description: The stun grenade causes temporary paralysis to all those in the blast radius, and does 20 damage points to surrounding enemies.
88885524.creator: ROBLOX

88885539.name: Airstrike
88885539.description: Your foes don't stand a chance when you call your pilot friends for reinforcements!  Use this to call a jet fighter that launches missiles at any area you designate.
88885539.creator: ROBLOX

89203876.name: Celestial Staff
89203876.description: Summon the rage of the skies!
89203876.creator: ROBLOX

89203895.name: Celestial Sword - A Walmart Exclusive
89203895.description: "Many that live deserve death. And some that die deserve life. Can you give it to them?"
89203895.creator: ROBLOX

89390416.name: Arachnix Drone
89390416.description: Black Phantom's drone is all kinds of trouble. This little spider-like drone multiplies itself and attacks your enemies. Play the Lego Hero Factory game on ROBLOX to win this prize!  http://www.roblox.com/LEGO-Hero-Factory-Breakout-place?id=32373412
89390416.creator: ROBLOX

89390459.name: Furno's Aquajet Pack and Plasma Gun
89390459.description: Furno's Aquajet Pack and Plasma Gun make it easy for him to fry any villain that gets in his way - especially Jawblade. Now you can fry your enemies too! Play the LegoHero Factory game on ROBLOX and win this prize!  http://www.roblox.com/LEGO-Hero-Factory-Breakout-place?id=32373412
89390459.creator: ROBLOX

89487903.name: Monster Axe
89487903.description: This axe is a monster!  Initial strike gives you 25 damage points and it continues to damage your opponent someone decides to remove the axe.
89487903.creator: ROBLOX

89487934.name: Medusa Head
89487934.description: Turn your enemies to stone for 5 seconds with this frightning Medusa head.
89487934.creator: ROBLOX

89488524.name: Ghost Minion
89488524.description: Heals you until you are more powerful than you ever were (150 hp).  But don't worry, if you die - he will avenge you!
89488524.creator: ROBLOX

89491407.name: Zombie Grip Bomb
89491407.description: Your enemies will try to scream, but terror will take the sound before they make it.  Toss this zombie bomb up to 100 studs away and drag your enemies six feet under.
89491407.creator: ROBLOX

89609598.name: Unit 3021
89609598.description: Why was six afraid of three thousand and twenty-one? Because three thousand and twenty-one was a robot.  A deadly robot that is not good at telling jokes.
89609598.creator: ROBLOX

89611361.name: Mystic Foreteller
89611361.description: He doesn't need to look at your palmst to see your future.
89611361.creator: ROBLOX

89615342.name: Feathered Crown
89615342.description: Each decade the last Ramuski bird sheds one pink feather. Its value is beyond measure.
89615342.creator: ROBLOX

89620675.name: Insectaur Helmet
89620675.description: He will crush you like the bug he is!
89620675.creator: ROBLOX

89621209.name: Green Plaid Cap
89621209.description: Classic plaid cap now in green!
89621209.creator: ROBLOX

89622944.name: BaseSkull Cap
89622944.description: It's like baseball but you know... not boring.
89622944.creator: ROBLOX

89623300.name: Steampunk Sidekick
89623300.description: By the late twentieth century, our time, a mythic time, we are all chimeras, theorized and fabricated hybrids of machine and organism; in short, we are cyborgs.
89623300.creator: ROBLOX

89623697.name: Wicked Wizard
89623697.description: The hat is as menacing as the wizard wearing it.
89623697.creator: ROBLOX

89624536.name: Evil Baseball Cap
89624536.description: This cap's got a mind of it's own!
89624536.creator: ROBLOX

89625422.name: DJ Headphones
89625422.description: For people who are serious about music.  Superior quality sound and great look.
89625422.creator: ROBLOX

89626088.name: Old Timey Farmer's Cap
89626088.description: Livin' off the land isn't easy...
89626088.creator: ROBLOX

90211299.name: Tiger Skin
90211299.description: When you are wearing this - you become stronger and faster.  Enemies will fear your touch as a single strike while wearing the skin will disarm them...literally.
90211299.creator: ROBLOX

90220371.name: Dart Trap
90220371.description: This ancient dart trap will shoot poisonous darts at anyone who crosses its path.  Each dart does 45 damage points.
90220371.creator: ROBLOX

90220438.name: Deluxe Hook Shot
90220438.description: This deluxe grappling hook will pull small unanchored object (like other players) towards you.  When used on larger items, it will propel you toward the item or place.
90220438.creator: ROBLOX

90242059.name: Adventure Island
90242059.description: Check out the latest and best new 2D game on ROBLOX.  Explore and survive on Adventure Island!  Use "ASWD" keys to move, "W" to jump, "Enter" to shoot, and "Enter" + "W" to superjump.
90242059.creator: ROBLOX

90718350.name: Bear Mine Gun
90718350.description: With the Bear Mine Gun, you strategically place two bear mines and remotely trigger them to come together at a high velocity for an explosive bear hug, instantly killing anyone caught in the middle.
90718350.creator: ROBLOX

90718505.name: Exponential Rocket Launcher
90718505.description: One rocket. Three rockets. Nine rockets.  The further your initial rocket travels, the more rockets it spawns, causing anywhere from 75 to 300 points of damage on impact, resulting in catastrophic damage for anyone that isnt you.
90718505.creator: ROBLOX

90718618.name: Anti-Ballistics Force Field
90718618.description: This force field deflects most projectiles launched at you and sends them sailing back at your opponents. Whats more, the reflected projectiles do an additional 50 damage points.
90718618.creator: ROBLOX

90718686.name: Conjuror's Fist
90718686.description: Instantly crushes anyone and anything unfortunate enough to be below where youve summoned it.
90718686.creator: ROBLOX

91294485.name: Hungry Lion Friend
91294485.description: He's hungry, but he's also your friend.  So he probably won't eat you.... probably.
91294485.creator: ROBLOX

91360028.name: Puppet Master
91360028.description: The puppet master runs the show!  Force others to do your bidding - and look silly.  Why?  No one asks the puppet master why.
91360028.creator: ROBLOX

91360052.name: Suit Up Gun
91360052.description: Bunny suit up! Dress other players in one of four embarrassing outfits.
91360052.creator: ROBLOX

91360081.name: Psychokinesis Glove
91360081.description: Move things with your mind...no problem. Okay you're actually moving it with the glove, but no one else has to know that.  Picks up near by players and rocks and hurls them to the ground.
91360081.creator: ROBLOX

91360104.name: Stop Hitting Yourself
91360104.description: Your enemies won't be able to stop themselves....from beating themselves up!  Does 10 damage per second.
91360104.creator: ROBLOX

91450692.name: Terratronic Health Core
91450692.description: Activate and toss this health core to form a healing circle, giving life to all within it.
91450692.creator: ROBLOX

91517984.name: Terratronic Power Sword - A Gamestop Exclusive
91517984.description: Your opponents don't stand a chance when you've got this sword equipped!
91517984.creator: ROBLOX

91518057.name: Terratronic Ray Gun - A Walmart Exclusive
91518057.description: Blast away anything that gets in your way.
91518057.creator: ROBLOX

91658290.name: Red Futurion Blaster
91658290.description: Part of the Red Futurion Package.
91658290.creator: ROBLOX

92142799.name: Phoenix
92142799.description: Equip the Phoenix and watch as it flies around you in a defensive circle, shooting at nearby enemies (25 damage per hit) for as long as five minutes. You can even have the Phoenix target specific enemies by clicking on them.
92142799.creator: ROBLOX

92142829.name: Rayvenge Sword
92142829.description: Get your revenge with the Rayvenge!  This sword makes short work of eliminating your enemies -the first attack removes your opponents limbs and does 27 damage with each subsequent hit doing 9 damage.
92142829.creator: ROBLOX

92142841.name: Artemis Bow
92142841.description: The Artemis Bow features two attack modes--you can charge a concentrated death shot that does up to 100 damage, or shoot in rapid fire mode for more arrows that deal 12 damage each.But that's not all - you can also use it to fly! When you jump, the Artemis Bow will grow wings and allow you to take flight.
92142841.creator: ROBLOX

92142950.name: Explosive Super Glider
92142950.description: With the click of a mouse you are airborne. While in the air, you can drop deadly bombs on your enemies. The bombs do 100 damage per hit, but they have a small radius.  Aim carefully.
92142950.creator: ROBLOX

92627975.name: Orinthian Falcon
92627975.description: A noble guardian to help protect you on your quest.  And by protect, I mean attack all enemies.  Circles above you and attacks those enemies unfortunate enough to be selected as his prey.  This falcon is from the future and features 5 different attack modes.
92627975.creator: ROBLOX

92627988.name: Orinthian Mace
92627988.description: This is no ordinary mace. Leaves behind a damaging trail of energy everywhere it is carried.
92627988.creator: ROBLOX

92628074.name: Orinthian Blaster 3777
92628074.description: Blast your enemies into the next galaxy  with the Orinthian blaster.  Does 35 damage per hit.
92628074.creator: ROBLOX

92628079.name: Orinthian Sword and Shield
92628079.description: Slash enemies with your futuristic sword or stop them dead in their tracks with a shield bash!  Activate the shield bash stun with a right click to stun enemies for 2 seconds.  When enemies are stunned, you can do extra damage!
92628079.creator: ROBLOX

93136666.name: Sword of the Seven Winters
93136666.description: Summon the blizzard of seven winters, causing snow for you and all around you.  Lucky for you, you knew the blizzard was coming and can move quickly in the snow that slows your enemies.  Does 20 damage.
93136666.creator: ROBLOX

93136674.name: Uppercut Sword
93136674.description: This gigantic sword will throw your enemies into the air and let you do as much damage as you can for 5 seconds.
93136674.creator: ROBLOX

93136746.name: Telamonster: the Chaos Edge
93136746.description: The lions sing and the hills take flight. The moon by day, and the sun by night. Blind woman, deaf man, jackdaw fool. Let the Lord of Chaos rule.
93136746.creator: ROBLOX

93136802.name: Amethyst Periastron Kappa
93136802.description: The sword men use to fight robot lions in space.
93136802.creator: ROBLOX

93528414.name: TMNT Skateboard
93528414.description: TMNT Skateboard: Grab a skateboard to ride through the streets of ROBLOX, TMNT style!
93528414.creator: ROBLOX

93536785.name: Zombie Axe
93536785.description: Does 15 damage per swipe and summons some Zombies to eat your enemies brains.
93536785.creator: ROBLOX

93536827.name: Zombie Bomb
93536827.description: This bomb summons powerful zombies to feast on your enemies.  Occasionally it will unlease a zombie explosion that kills on contact.
93536827.creator: ROBLOX

93536844.name: Zombie Launcher
93536844.description: Shoot powerful hungry zombies at your enemies.  Watch and laugh as they chase your foes and bite them - stealing 10hp each second.
93536844.creator: ROBLOX

93536867.name: Zombification Injection
93536867.description: Steal other people's life force to transform yourself into a powerful and angry zombie.  As a zombie, use your powerful hammer to do 40 damage per hit to other players.
93536867.creator: ROBLOX

93667422.name: Splinter's Staff
93667422.description: Master Splinter is the Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Sensei, teaching them how to fight and protect their home. Unlock his character in TMNT: Turtle Trouble and win his staff!
93667422.creator: ROBLOX

93709266.name: Polar Bear Cub
93709266.description: All the fun of a polar bear with none of the aggression.
93709266.creator: ROBLOX

93722443.name: Skeleton Bone Staff - A Gamestop Exclusive
93722443.description: Why waste ammo when you can use bones?  Fires bones that do damage at your enemies.
93722443.creator: ROBLOX

93722515.name: Halloween Transmuter
93722515.description: Tranform anyone and everyone into spooky Halloween items!
93722515.creator: ROBLOX

93725362.name: Sword Of The Behemoth - a Walmart Exclusive
93725362.description: "Hark! Hark to the wind! / 'Tis the night, they say, / When all souls come back from the far away-- / The dead, forgotten this many a day!"
93725362.creator: ROBLOX

93746675.name: Crash
93746675.description:
Get Crash and your in-game wingman! You never know what he's going to do next. 
Brand New Crash & Bernstein Mondays at 8:30PM/7:30c on Disney XD!
93746675.creator: ROBLOX

93772507.name: Crash Shirt
93772507.description: Look like Crash by picking up this awesome virtual Crash t-shirt! FACE SLAM!
93772507.creator: ROBLOX

94119269.name: Molecular Atomizer
94119269.description: Protect yourself with this Molecular Atomizer, the best defense against all the zombies and werewolves running through ROBLOX. And don't forget to watch the premiere of Girl vs. Monster Friday, October 12 at 8p/7c on Disney Channel!
94119269.creator: ROBLOX

94233286.name: M1 Garand
94233286.description: This M1 includes an eight-round clip, with bullets that deal 35 points of damage to the body and insta-kills for head shots.
94233286.creator: ROBLOX

94233344.name: Trench Warfare Shotgun
94233344.description: The Trench Gun shoots up to 20 bullets in a single round, with a wide spray around your target, making it super easy to hit nearby enemies. There are only six rounds in a clip, so time your reloads wisely!
94233344.creator: ROBLOX

94233367.name: Ghost Blaster
94233367.description: This blaster will down your foes with just one hit!  But that's not all - your foe will come back as  your ghost minion and attack other players for 30 seconds.
94233367.creator: ROBLOX

94233391.name: Ghost Dragon
94233391.description: Let the Ghost Dragon do your bidding!  Flies above you and sends out 100 points of damage on your behalf.
94233391.creator: ROBLOX

94333296.name: Nightfall Elixir
94333296.description: It's that time of the day when the sun goes down.
94333296.creator: ROBLOX

94794774.name: Crescendo, The Soul Stealer
94794774.description: Forged with fiery flames and a demon's eye the Crescendo ascends from its ancient sleep with a thundering tone.
94794774.creator: ROBLOX

94794833.name: Cloak of the Undying
94794833.description: Adorn this cloak, and none shall stand in thou's way, m'lord.
94794833.creator: ROBLOX

94794847.name: Vampire Vanquisher: Sword and Shield
94794847.description: Where the sword goes the shield follows, through the valley.
94794847.creator: ROBLOX

95258660.name: Explosive Spy Pen
95258660.description: This pen is certainly mightier than a sword!  Click twice and throw the pen for an explosive surprise.  Well it's not a surprise to you - you know it's an explosive spy pen.
95258660.creator: ROBLOX

95354259.name: Forbidden Box
95354259.description: You know that box your gramps told you never to open?  Now you know why!  The Forbidden Box will summon several violent beasts, which will hunt down any player, friend or foe, who lays eyes on it or falls within its area of effect. You can spawn up to four monsters at a time, each of which is capable of dealing 10 points of damage per second.
95354259.creator: ROBLOX

95354268.name: Trollamom
95354268.description: Trollamom is sure to scare your foes with her deadly "mom glare".  You know the look, one that only moms can give where it feels like they're shooting lasers out of their eyes? Well this mom actually shoots lasers.  But that's not all! After her deadly glare, Trollamom summons Trollamon, who will throw pieces of fried chicken at your enemies. Aren't moms great?
95354268.creator: ROBLOX

95354288.name: Luger Pistol
95354288.description: The WW2 Luger is an old school war relic that lets you target different limbs for different affects. Shoot a player in the leg, and they'll walk a quarter slower. Shoot them in the arm, and they'll drop their weapon. Body shots do 20 hit points of damage.
95354288.creator: ROBLOX

95354304.name: Sten Gun
95354304.description: Fires 500 rounds a minute, with over-sized, 50-round clips. While the strong recoil makes it inaccurate at long ranges, you should be ashamed of yourself if you unload fifty bullets and hit nothing but air. Each bullet does 15 points of damage. Multiply that by 50 rounds and you've got enough damage to defeat more than a couple foes.
95354304.creator: ROBLOX

95484098.name: Werewolf Claws
95484098.description: Lunge, slash and dash at your opponents.  At night - become faster and stronger just like the rest of your pack!  These werewolf claws came out of the Gift of Clawed Combat on October 19th. 2012.
95484098.creator: ROBLOX

95484354.name: Misfortune Cookie
95484354.description: It's not going to bring you luck but it might be fun.
95484354.creator: ROBLOX

95951270.name: Korblox Bone & Arrow
95951270.description: Its a classic longbow, with a certain distinction: its constructed of the finest, most durable bone. Take out one of your foes with this weapon and their body instantly turns into a skeleton.
95951270.creator: ROBLOX

95951291.name: Skeleton King's Sword
95951291.description: This sword features three unique swings and a spin move (tap W twice and left-click), each of which has a 20% chance of cracking an enemys joints. As if that wasnt enough, each attack has a 22% chance of being critical (2.25x damage). Normal attacks do 25 damage, landing critical attacks at about 56. Bone has never been so dangerous.
95951291.creator: ROBLOX

95951330.name: Skeleton Scythe
95951330.description: Swing at your enemies to do 20 damage per hit.  Press "E" three times to summon a small army.
95951330.creator: ROBLOX

95951359.name: Skeleton Bomb
95951359.description: Fling deadly bone shrapnel at your enemies for fun and profit!  Okay probably just for fun.
95951359.creator: ROBLOX

96092647.name: Korblox Skeleton Wraith
96092647.description: He was alive when they put him in the box!  Now he's your official Korblox guardian pet.  The Korblox Skeleton Wraith came out of the Gift of the Korbloxian on October 26th, 2012
96092647.creator: ROBLOX

96095042.name: Sorcus' Chair
96095042.description: This is how he rolls...and trolls....  Sorcus' Chair came out of the Surly Gift of Sorcus II on October 26th, 2012.
96095042.creator: ROBLOX

96493688.name: Autumn Shuriken - A Target Exclusive
96493688.description: Oh wow - that leaf is travelling fast!  That's because it's not a leaf - it's a deadly shuriken.  Get this item when you redeem a card from Target in November.
96493688.creator: ROBLOX

96501417.name: Autumn Oak Staff - A Walmart Exclusive
96501417.description: Summon vines that will wrap your enemies in trouble!
96501417.creator: ROBLOX

96501454.name: Lightning Bolt Sword- A Gamestop Exclusive
96501454.description: Your foes will have more than a sword to contend with when you wield this weapon.
96501454.creator: ROBLOX

100290429.name: iFace
100290429.description: ROBLOX's first iOS exclusive face.  Get it soon - only available through our mobile app. Get more details here - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/roblox-mobile/id431946152?mt=8
100290429.creator: ROBLOX

100966309.name: Color Changing SG {Black Pants}[READ DESC] ON SALE
100966309.description:
